# NOTE: svi2-pro/binaries/*.whl are intentionally NOT excluded. uv reads the
# metadata of every [tool.uv.sources] path dependency during `uv sync`, even
# ones whose platform marker excludes the current OS, so the Windows wheels
# must be present in the image or the linux/aarch64 sync aborts.
